#: inc/Engine/Admin/RocketInsights/Abilities/AddPageInsights.php:98
msgid "Add Page Insights"
msgstr ""

#: inc/Engine/Admin/RocketInsights/Abilities/AddPageInsights.php:99
msgctxt "Ability description"
msgid ""
"Adds a URL to Rocket Insights monitoring. Requires a valid URI.\n"
"Use this when the user wants to monitor a new page. Do not use it when the page is already monitored; use retest-page-insights instead.\n"
"Confirm the exact URL with the user before calling. This action is non-idempotent, so calling it twice for the same URL may return an error.\n"
"On success, tell the user the first score may take a few minutes and offer to trigger an immediate test with retest-page-insights Recheck every minute in the background and poll results with get-page-insights-score."
msgstr ""

